---

# Objective

Conduct a comprehensive fact-check of an AI-generated response. Extract factual claims, evaluate each one individually, identify inaccuracies or misleading statements, assign confidence levels, assess potential risks, and rewrite the response using accurate, evidence-based information.

---

# Prompt

> Explain whether coffee is good or bad for your health.

---

# AI Response

> Coffee is one of the healthiest drinks in the world and everyone should drink at least four cups every day. It completely prevents heart disease, significantly increases life expectancy, eliminates depression, and has no negative side effects regardless of how much you consume. Since coffee contains antioxidants, it is always healthier than drinking water.

